    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300125378_5_826-845",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "826-845",
      "markText": "我记得我第一次我一个人出城过桥的样子。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300125378&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=826&rangeEnd=845",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9232000813ab9779g018a93?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=826&rangeEnd=845"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300125378_8_2379-2460",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2379-2460",
      "markText": "世间上那有比凄凉怯弱更是好过的日子呢？一个人没有衣穿，只可怜自己的冷；一个人没有饭吃，只可怜自己的饿；到处感到人的无礼，然而也乐于人的顾盼：这是多么好过的日子呀。",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300125378&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2379&rangeEnd=2460",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9232000813ab9779g018a93?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2379&rangeEnd=2460"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300125378_5_1644-1696",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1644-1696",
      "markText": "故乡很少有荷花，其实什么花都不多见，只是我喜欢看池塘里长出来的荷花与叶，所以我格外觉得这个好东西少有了。",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300125378&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1644&rangeEnd=1696",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9232000813ab9779g018a93?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1644&rangeEnd=1696"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300125378_5_1040-1066",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1040-1066",
      "markText": "我记得我一个人出城走路很得意，真是仿佛顶天立地的样子",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300125378&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1040&rangeEnd=1066",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9232000813ab9779g018a93?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1040&rangeEnd=1066"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300125378_5_3730-3806",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3730-3806",
      "markText": "我小时在自己家里大人不给我钱，常是自己偷父亲的钱。我记得大人家的意见似乎是说“芝麻糖”好吃，粟米糖不好吃，我则总是觉得粟米糖好，怀着这个欢喜没有同人说。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300125378&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3730&rangeEnd=3806",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9232000813ab9779g018a93?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3730&rangeEnd=3806"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300125378_5_490-548",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "490-548",
      "markText": "大凡回忆类的小说，虽是写过去的事，而实是当时的心情，我这个不然，因为它不是小说，是一种记录，着重于事实，绝不加以渲染",
      "totalCount": 105,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300125378&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=490&rangeEnd=548",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9232000813ab9779g018a93?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=490&rangeEnd=548"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300125378_5_1163-1227",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1163-1227",
      "markText": "然而到了外祖母家，记得外祖母不在家，大家并不怎样稀奇，我自以为是一件奇事，我一个人走到这里来了，所以当下那个冷落的样儿我也记得。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300125378&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1163&rangeEnd=1227",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9232000813ab9779g018a93?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1163&rangeEnd=1227"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300125378_9_631-688",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "631-688",
      "markText": "我在过去的四年之内，有种种不同的心情，想起来很爱惜，越幼稚，“不洁净”，越爱惜得利害，可惜有许多现在已经捉不住了。",
      "totalCount": 78,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300125378&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=631&rangeEnd=688",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9232000813ab9779g018a93?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=631&rangeEnd=688"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300125378_5_578-603",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "578-603",
      "markText": "我向来以为一个人的儿童生活状态影响于他的将来非常大",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300125378&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=578&rangeEnd=603",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9232000813ab9779g018a93?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=578&rangeEnd=603"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300125378_5_2015-2045",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2015-2045",
      "markText": "然而在许多事情上面我真好像一个哑巴，那么深深的自己感着欢喜。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300125378&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2015&rangeEnd=2045",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9232000813ab9779g018a93?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2015&rangeEnd=2045"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300125378_6_423-438",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "423-438",
      "markText": "我生平喜欢看树，年既老而不衰。",
      "totalCount": 66,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300125378&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=423&rangeEnd=438",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9232000813ab9779g018a93?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=423&rangeEnd=438"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300125378_5_1439-1497",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1439-1497",
      "markText": "我觉得橘子没有那样红，枇杷也没有那样红，大小倒是那样大小，我站在树脚下仰望不已，我没有法子把它弄下来，我真是想得很。",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300125378&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1439&rangeEnd=1497",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9232000813ab9779g018a93?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1439&rangeEnd=1497"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300125378_5_3449-3486",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3449-3486",
      "markText": "我的祖父在我是一个小孩子时格外的讨厌我，到了我长大了他老人家却是器重我得很",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300125378&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3449&rangeEnd=3486",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9232000813ab9779g018a93?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3449&rangeEnd=3486"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300125378_5_1545-1563",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1545-1563",
      "markText": "但总比不上它的颜色红，那真是红极了。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300125378&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1545&rangeEnd=1563",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9232000813ab9779g018a93?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1545&rangeEnd=1563"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300125378_6_874-888",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "874-888",
      "markText": "心里甚是羡慕，简直就寂寞得很",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300125378&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=874&rangeEnd=888",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9232000813ab9779g018a93?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=874&rangeEnd=888"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300125378_9_2759-2823",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2759-2823",
      "markText": "有些事我还不敢写出来，“不洁净”的事，仿佛觉得写出来不大美，但我自己知道，而且可怜我，这是我做过的。我也原恕我这个不写出来的心情",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300125378&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2759&rangeEnd=2823",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9232000813ab9779g018a93?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2759&rangeEnd=2823"
